FTK -- Fortran ToolKit

bin         executables.
gnss        GNSS utilities 
sar         InSAR utilities
lib         FTK common library
external    Tools by others
  ***Copyrights of programs in external belong to other authors!!***
compiler.config  Configuration for path and fortran/c compilers

To compile and install FTK:
  make
Use
  make install
to copy executables to $iGPS/ftk/bin directory.
Add this directory to you shell's searching path, e.g., 
for bash in ~/.bashrc:
  PATH=${PATH}:${iGPS}/ftk/bin
for csh in ~/.cshrc:
  set path = ($path ${iGPS}/ftk/bin
where $iGPS is the iGPS's root directory.
